    java.io.Serializable
    封闭类:
    FieldAccessor<T,F>

    static final class FieldAccessor.SimpleTupleFieldAccessor<T extends Tuple,F>
extends FieldAccessor<T,F>
    There are two versions of TupleFieldAccessor, differing in whether there is an other FieldAccessor nested inside. The no inner accessor version is probably a little faster.
